    <verse number="14" style="v" sid="2SA 11:14" />¶ And it came to pass in the <char style="w" strong="H1242">morning</char>, that <char style="w" strong="H1732">David</char> <char style="w" strong="H3789">wrote</char> a <char style="w" strong="H5612">letter</char> to <char style="w" strong="H3097">Joab</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H7971">sent</char> <char style="add">it</char> by the <char style="w" strong="H3027">hand</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0223">Uriah</char>. <verse eid="2SA 11:14" /><verse number="15" style="v" sid="2SA 11:15" />And he <char style="w" strong="H3789">wrote</char> in the <char style="w" strong="H5612">letter</char>, <char style="w" strong="H0559">saying</char>, <char style="w" strong="H3051">Set</char> ye <char style="w" strong="H0223">Uriah</char> in the <char style="w" strong="H6440">forefront</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H2389">hottest</char> <char style="w" strong="H4421">battle</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H7725">retire</char> ye from <char style="w" strong="H0310">him</char>, that he may be <char style="w" strong="H5221">smitten</char>, and <char style="w" strong="H4191">die</char>.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11.15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">hottest: Heb. strong</char></note><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">11.15 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">from him: Heb. from after him</char></note> <verse eid="2SA 11:15" /><verse number="16" style="v" sid="2SA 11:16" />And it came to pass, when <char style="w" strong="H3097">Joab</char> <char style="w" strong="H8104">observed</char> the <char style="w" strong="H5892">city</char>, that he <char style="w" strong="H5414">assigned</char> <char style="w" strong="H0223">Uriah</char> unto a <char style="w" strong="H4725">place</char> where he <char style="w" strong="H3045">knew</char> that <char style="w" strong="H2428">valiant</char> <char style="w" strong="H0582">men</char> <char style="add">were<