thy <char style="w" strong="H0802">wives</char> in the <char style="w" strong="H5869">sight</char> of this <char style="w" strong="H8121">sun</char>. <verse eid="2SA 12:11" /><verse number="12" style="v" sid="2SA 12:12" />For thou <char style="w" strong="H6213">didst</char> <char style="add">it</char> <char style="w" strong="H5643">secretly</char>: but I will <char style="w" strong="H6213">do</char> this <char style="w" strong="H1697">thing</char> before all <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char>, and before the <char style="w" strong="H8121">sun</char>. <verse eid="2SA 12:12" /><verse number="13" style="v" sid="2SA 12:13" />And <char style="w" strong="H1732">David</char> <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char> unto <char style="w" strong="H5416">Nathan</char>, I have <char style="w" strong="H2398">sinned</char> against the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char>. And <char style="w" strong="H5416">Nathan</char> <char style="w" strong="H0559">said</char> unto <char style="w" strong="H1732">David</char>, The <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> also hath put <char style="w" strong="H5674">away</char> thy <char style="w" strong="H2403">sin</char>; thou shalt not <char style="w" strong="H4191">die</char>. <verse eid="2SA 12:13" /><verse number="14" style="v" sid="2SA 12:14" /><char style="w" strong="H0657">Howbeit</char>, because by this <char style="w" strong="H1697">deed</char> thou hast <char style="w" strong="H5006">given</char> great <char style="w" strong="H5006">occasion</char> to the <char style="w" strong="H0341">enemies</char> of the <char style="nd"><char style="w" strong="H3068">LORD</char></char> to <char style="w" strong="H5006">blaspheme</char>, the <char style="w" strong="H1121">child</char> also <char style="add">that is</char> <char style="w" strong="H3209">born</char> unto thee shall <char style="w" strong="H4191">surely</char> <char style="w" strong="H4191">die</char>.<verse eid="2SA 