eid="2SA 20:22" /></para>
  <para style="p">
    <verse number="23" style="v" sid="2SA 20:23" />¶ Now <char style="w" strong="H3097">Joab</char> <char style="add">was</char> over all the <char style="w" strong="H6635">host</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3478">Israel</char>: and <char style="w" strong="H1141">Benaiah</char> the <char style="w" strong="H1121">son</char> of <char style="w" strong="H3077">Jehoiada</char> <char style="add">was</char> over the <char style="w" strong="H3774">Cherethites</char> and over the <char style="w" strong="H6432">Pelethites</char>: <verse eid="2SA 20:23" /><verse number="24" style="v" sid="2SA 20:24" />And <char style="w" strong="H0151">Adoram</char> <char style="add">was</char> over the <char style="w" strong="H4522">tribute</char>: and <char style="w" strong="H3092">Jehoshaphat</char> the <char style="w" strong="H1121">son</char> of <char style="w" strong="H0286">Ahilud</char> <char style="add">was</char> <char style="w" strong="H2142">recorder</char>:<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">20.24 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">recorder: or, remembrancer</char></note> <verse eid="2SA 20:24" /><verse number="25" style="v" sid="2SA 20:25" />And <char style="w" strong="H7864">Sheva</char> <char style="add">was</char> <char style="w" strong="H5608">scribe</char>: and <char style="w" strong="H6659">Zadok</char> and <char style="w" strong="H0054">Abiathar</char> <char style="add">were</char> the <char style="w" strong="H3548">priests</char>: <verse eid="2SA 20:25" /><verse number="26" style="v" sid="2SA 20:26" />And <char style="w" strong="H5896">Ira</char> also the <char style="w" strong="H2972">Jairite</char> was a chief <char style="w" strong="H3548">ruler</char> about <char style="w" strong="H1732">David</char>.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">20.26 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">a chief…: or, a prince</char></note><verse eid="2SA 20:26" /></para>
