    <verse number="8" style="v" sid="2SA 23:8" />¶ These <char style="add">be</char> the <char style="w" strong="H8034">names</char> of the mighty <char style="w" strong="H1368">men</char> whom <char style="w" strong="H1732">David</char> had: The <char style="w" strong="H8461">Tachmonite</char> that <char style="w" strong="H3427">sat</char> in the <char style="w" strong="H7675">seat</char>, <char style="w" strong="H7218">chief</char> among the <char style="w" strong="H7991">captains</char>; the same <char style="add">was</char> <char style="w" strong="H5722">Adino</char> the <char style="w" strong="H6112">Eznite</char>: <char style="add">he lift up his spear</char> against <char style="w" strong="H8083">eight</char> <char style="w" strong="H3967">hundred</char>, whom he <char style="w" strong="H2491">slew</char> at <char style="w" strong="H0259">one</char> <char style="w" strong="H6471">time</char>.<note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">23.8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">The Tachmonite…: or, Joshebbassebet the Tachmonite, head of the three</char></note><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">23.8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">whom he…: Heb. slain</char></note><note caller="+" style="f"><char style="fr" closed="false">23.8 </char><char style="ft" closed="false">1ch 11:11 he lift…: from whom he…: Heb. slain</char></note> <verse eid="2SA 23:8" /><verse number="9" style="v" sid="2SA 23:9" />And <char style="w" strong="H0310">after</char> him <char style="add">was</char> <char style="w" strong="H0499">Eleazar</char> the <char style="w" strong="H1121">son</char> of <char style="w" strong="H1734">Dodo</char> the <char style="w" strong="H0266">Ahohite</char>, <char style="add">one</char> of the <char style="w" strong="H7969">three</char> mighty <char style="w" strong="H1368">men</char> with <char style="w" strong="H1732">David</char>, when they <char style="w" strong="H2778">defied</char> the <char style="w" strong="H